<wsp:Policy xmlns:L7p="http://www.layer7tech.com/ws/policy" xmlns:wsp="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2002/12/policy">
    <wsp:All wsp:Usage="Required">
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="================================================================"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="APIIDA Service - APIIDA Profiling API"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="Service to retrieve profiling data cached on gateway."/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="PARAMETERS:"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="clearCache [true|false]- (Optional, default=false) Query Parameter to delete cache after retrieval."/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="removePrevious [true|false]- (Optional, default=false) Remove events since last service call (This is generic and not caller specific)."/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="NOTES:"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="- Uses CWP: apiida.utils.maxCacheAge"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="- Uses CWP: apiida.utils.maxCacheSize"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue=" - No Authentication checking of any kind. Not needed for POC."/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue=" - No proper Method/URL/Header checking. Not needed for POC."/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="================================================================"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue=" "/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="------------------------------------------------------------------------"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="Process Events Cache"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <L7p:CommentAssertion>
            <L7p:Comment stringValue="------------------------------------------------------------------------"/>
        </L7p:CommentAssertion>
        <wsp:OneOrMore wsp:Usage="Required">
            <wsp:All wsp:Usage="Required">
                <L7p:CommentAssertion>
                    <L7p:Comment stringValue=" "/>
                </L7p:CommentAssertion>
                <L7p:CommentAssertion>
                    <L7p:Comment stringValue="Retrieve Cache"/>
                </L7p:CommentAssertion>
                <L7p:CommentAssertion>
                    <L7p:Comment stringValue=" "/>
                </L7p:CommentAssertion>
                <L7p:Encapsulated>
                    <L7p:EncapsulatedAssertionConfigGuid stringValue="590ca436-8955-4ce1-a2ff-e1721279d816"/>
                    <L7p:EncapsulatedAssertionConfigName stringValue="APIIDA Utility - Load Cache"/>
                    <L7p:Parameters mapValue="included">
                        <L7p:entry>
                            <L7p:key stringValue="apiida.id"/>
                            <L7p:value stringValue="apiida-utils-profilingEventCache"/>
                        </L7p:entry>
                        <L7p:entry>

                            <L7p:value stringValue="apiida"/>
                        </L7p:entry>
                        <L7p:entry>

                        </L7p:entry>
                    </L7p:Parameters>

                <wsp:OneOrMore wsp:Usage="Required">
                    <wsp:All wsp:Usage="Required">
                        <L7p:ComparisonAssertion>
                            <L7p:Expression1 stringValue="${request.http.parameters.clearCache}"/>

                                <L7p:item binary="included">

                                </L7p:item>

                                    <L7p:value stringValue="apiida-utils-profilingEventCache"/>
                                </L7p:entry>
                                <L7p:entry>
                                    <L7p:key stringValue="apiida.key"/>
                                    <L7p:value stringValue="apiida"/>
                                </L7p:entry>
                            </L7p:Parameters>

                    </wsp:All>
                    <L7p:TrueAssertion/>
                    <L7p:assertionComment>
                        <L7p:Properties mapValue="included">

                                <L7p:value stringValue="[Delete Cache if needed]"/>

                        </L7p:Properties>
                    </L7p:assertionComment>
                </wsp:OneOrMore>
                <L7p:SetVariable>
                    <L7p:Base64Expression stringValue="JHthcGlpZGEudmFyLmNhY2hlUGF5bG9hZC5tYWlucGFydH0="/>

                                    <L7p:EncapsulatedAssertionConfigGuid stringValue="590ca436-8955-4ce1-a2ff-e1721279d816"/>
                                    <L7p:EncapsulatedAssertionConfigName stringValue="APIIDA Utility - Load Cache"/>
                                    <L7p:Parameters mapValue="included">

encassConfigs.name: APIIDA Utility - Load Cache
encassConfigs.description:
APIIDA Utility
Load a cache payload, with optional exires string, from cache.

encassConfigs.name: APIIDA Utility - Store Cache
encassConfigs.description:
APIIDA Utility
Store a message payload to cache, with optional exires string.

encassConfigs.name: APIIDA Utility - Log Internal String
encassConfigs.description:
APIIDA Utility
Log an internal string with optional Post-String.

encassConfigs.name: APIIDA Utility - Delete Cache
encassConfigs.description:
APIIDA Utility
Delete a cache entry.

encassConfigs.name: APIIDA Utility - Start Profiling
encassConfigs.description:
APIIDA Utility
Start a profiling event with given name.

encassConfigs.name: APIIDA Utility - Stop Profiling
encassConfigs.description:
APIIDA Utility
Stop a profiling event with given name.

encassConfigs.name: APIIDA Utility - Logger
encassConfigs.description:
APIIDA Utility
Log a message following logging profile rules.
